nsing">VITO</a></BR>', 'EUMETCast, EUMETCast-Africa, EUMETCast-Europe', 'EUMETSAT Data Channel 3,', '<a href="http://eoportal.eumetsat.int/userMgmt">EO Portal Registration</a></BR>', NULL, NULL, 'VGT4AFRICA_LAI_20060101_Africa.ZIP, VGT4AFRICA_BIOQ_20060101_Africa.ZIP,', '33.0 MB,', '3 (per month),', 'copyright', 'copyright', 'restricted', '2009-08-31', 'EO_EUM_DAT_SPOT_LAI.html', 'EO:EUM:DAT:SPOT:LAI');
