Data: Index of files</a></BR>', 'EUMETCast, EUMETCast-Africa, EUMETCast-Americas, EUMETCast-Europe', 'EUMETSAT Data Channel 8,', '<a href="http://eoportal.eumetsat.int/userMgmt">EO Portal Registration</a></BR><a href="ftp://oceans.gsfc.nasa.gov/MODISA/Mapped/Daily/4/CHLO/">NASA FTP</a></BR><a href="http://oceandata.sci.gsfc.nasa.gov/MODISA/Mapped/Daily/4km/chlor/2010/">Index of files</a></BR>', NULL, NULL, 'A2010001.L3m_DAY_CHL_chlor_a_4km.bz2, A2010001.L3m_DAY_CHL_chlor_a_4km.bz2,', '3.5 MB, 3.5 MB,', '1 (per day), 1 (per day),', 'copyright', 'copyright', NULL, '2013-02-04', 'EO_EUM_DAT_AQUA_CHLORA.html', 'EO:EUM:DAT:AQUA:CHLORA');
