loud Analysis - Factsheet</a></BR><a href="http://www.eumetsat.int/website/wcm/idc/idcplg?IdcService=GET_FILE&dDocName=PDF_SCI_97181_MSG-CLOUD-PROPS&RevisionSelectionMethod=LatestReleased&Rendition=Web">Study on Cloud Properties derived from Meteosat Second Generation Observations (RAL, 2001)</a></BR>', 'EUMETCast, EUMETCast-Europe', 'EUMETSAT Data Channel 4,', '<a href="http://eoportal.eumetsat.int/userMgmt">EO Portal Registration</a></BR><a href="http://eoportal.eumetsat.int/userMgmt/protected/dataCentre.faces?acronym=MSGOCAE">EUMETSAT Data Centre</a></BR>', NULL, NULL, 'L-000-MSG3__-MPEF________-OCAE_____-000010___-20306110100-__, L-000-MSG3__-MPEF________-OCAE_____-PRO______-20306102200-__, MSG3-SEVI-MSGOCAE-0100-0100-20130626130000.00000000Z-1068508.grb,', '39 MB, 36 MB,', '24 (per day), 24 (per day),', 'copyright', 'copyright', NULL, '2013-12-04', 'EO_EUM_DAT_MSG_OCA.html', 'EO:EUM:DAT:MSG:OCA');
